      "Delivery preferences include at minimum: time window, signature requirement, and safe-place instructions",
      "The existing single-recipient data model stores recipient fields directly on the Shipment entity (not as a separate Recipient entity), requiring a structural migration",
      "Partner APIs are contractually bound and cannot be changed without coordination",
      "The 2M record migration must be zero-downtime"
    ]
  },

