      ],
      "recommendation": "Option C — the product team must enumerate delivery preferences explicitly. This determines the Recipient entity schema and has downstream effects on routing, notifications, and partner APIs."
    },
    {
      "type": "ambiguity",
      "description": "No concept of 'Primary Recipient' is defined, yet backward compatibility with partner APIs and shipment-level decisions (cancellation, rerouting, billing contact) require one. Is the first recipient primary? Is it explicitly designated? Can it change?",
      "affected_stakeholders": ["External API partners", "Customer support", "Finance/billing"],
